<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Oatmail</title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/bootstrap.min.css' />      
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12-md">
          <h1>Oatmail uses <a href="https://tent.io">tent</a> to store, send and recieve your emails</h1>
          <p>We don't display ads, harvest content or undermine your privacy</p>
          <hr />
          <p>Enter your tent entity below to sign in to your mailbox or register your Oatmail address.</p>          
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row padding-bottom-100">
        <div class="col-12-md">    
          <form name="tentUserReg" class="form-inline" action="/authenticate" method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">
              <input type="text" class="form-control" id="entitySignUpInput" name="entity" placeholder="e.g. https://pauljohncleary.cupcake.is" />
            </div>            
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary pull-right">Sign In / Register</button>
          </form>          
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12-md">
         <p><strong>Oatmail is under heavy development, nothing is guaranteed and everything can change.</strong></p>
         <p>If you don't already have a tent entity, you can get one at <a href="https://cupcake.io/">Cupcake.io</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
       
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12-md">
          <hr />
          <p>Oatmail is being built by <a href="https://pauljohncleary.cupcake.is/">^pauljohncleary.cupcake.is</a><p>
          <p>Feel free to checkout and comment on the <a href="https://trello.com/b/De5UNpdN/oatmail-roadmap">Oatmail Roadmap</a></p>
          <p>Source code is on github: <a href="https://github.com/pauljohncleary/oatmail"></a> We currently use <a href="http://www.mailgun.com/">Mailgun</a> as our mail server (there are plans to change this).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>